      "writtenOn": "2016-07-18T22:49:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm, it seems like we can\u0027t really do it this way, as I tried moving the initialization code off of qemu-setup.cpp in qemu2, and then starting the emulator would sometimes fail an assertion in wanted_pipes_pop_first: that pipe-\u003ewanted_prev \u003d\u003d NULL.\n\nSo I ended up making DeviceOperation a virtual member and keeping the two-stage initialization for the VmLock, at least for now.",
      "parentUuid": "faa1580d_48c94ab9",
